name: Conceited Software
tag_list: mac, iphone, software, chat, irc, health
overview:
Conceited Software is an independent development studio focused on creating excellent applications for the Mac and iPhone platforms.

Conceited Software aims at bringing together our expertise in both Mac and iPhone development to continuously create the richest, most intuitive and powerful applications for those platforms.

Our team of engineers makes every effort to keep our software fun and easy to use while being constantly attentive to every last detail. We are also available to develop custom applications, so please don’t hesitate to get in touch if you have an idea to submit or a project to discuss!

Technologies on the Mac and the iPhone offer incredible potential for exciting new apps. Many projects and ideas are being sorted out and actively developed as we speak, and we look forward to introducing them to you in the upcoming weeks.
